---
title: Sriracha Pork Noodles with Bok Choy and Sesame
description: We love good Sriracha Pork Noodles and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sriracha-pork-noodles-1e9c05e8-29a28257.jpg
